Invocation Name: daily catto
des: Want to learn more about cat breeds? This is the skill for you! Every day of the year you will receive a different cat breed with a short description straight from WIkipedia. You can also ask for additional breeds if one a day isn't enough for you.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
